---
<section class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative py-32 bg-[#000000] text-[#fcd34d] overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Starfield Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
        {Array.from({ length: 100 }).map(() => (
            <div class="absolute rounded-full bg-white"
                 style={`left: ${Math.random() * 100}%; top: ${Math.random() * 100}%; width: ${Math.random() * 2}px; height: ${Math.random() * 2}px; opacity: ${Math.random()};`}>
            </div>
        ))}
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
            
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-8">
                <span class="text-[#fbbf24] font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase border-b border-[#b45309] pb-2">El Mapa Galáctico</span>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif italic text-[#fffbeb]">El Disco de Oro</h2>
                
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed font-serif text-[#fde68a]/90">
                    ¿Cómo le dices a un extraterrestre dónde vives? No puedes usar "izquierda" o "derecha". 
                    Necesitas referencias universales.
                </p>
                
                <div class="bg-[#451a03]/40 p-6 rounded-sm border border-[#f59e0b]/30 mt-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
                    <h3 class="text-[#fcd34d] font-bold mb-2">Faros de Púlsares</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-[#fde68a] leading-relaxed">
                        En la cubierta de las Voyager, grabamos un mapa. 
                        El centro somos nosotros. Las líneas conectan con 14 púlsares (estrellas muertas que giran).
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#fbbf24] italic">
                        La longitud de cada línea en código binario indica la frecuencia del púlsar. 
                        Es la dirección postal más ambiciosa jamás escrita.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex justify-center relative h-[400px]">
                <!-- Pulsar Map Visualization (SVG) -->
                <div class="relative w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" class="w-full h-full overflow-visible">
                        <!-- The Map Center (Earth/Sun) -->
                        <g transform="translate(200, 200)">
                            <!-- Center Dot -->
                            <circle r="2" fill="#fcd34d" />
                            
                            <!-- Pulsar Lines -->
                            <!-- Randomly generated lines radiating out -->
                            {Array.from({ length: 14 }).map(() => {
                                const angle = Math.random() * 360;
                                const length = 50 + Math.random() * 100;
                                return (
                                    <g transform={`rotate(${angle})`}>
                                        <!-- The Line -->
                                        <line x1="0" y1="0" x2={length} y2="0" stroke="#fcd34d" stroke-width="1" />
                                        <!-- The Binary Code (Dashes) -->
                                        <line x1={length} y1="0" x2={length + 20} y2="0" stroke="#fcd34d" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="2 2" opacity="0.5" />
                                        <!-- Pulsar Star at end -->
                                        <circle cx={length + 25} cy="0" r="1.5" fill="#fff" class="animate-pulse-star" style={`animation-duration: ${0.5 + Math.random()}s`} />
                                    </g>
                                );
                            })}
                            
                            <!-- Hydrogen Atom Reference (Bottom Right usually, but simplified here) -->
                            <!-- Maybe just the map is enough iconic imagery -->
                        </g>

                        <!-- Golden Record Texture Overlay (Subtle rings) -->
                        <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="180" fill="none" stroke="#fcd34d" stroke-width="40" opacity="0.05" />
                        <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="100" fill="none" stroke="#fcd34d" stroke-width="20" opacity="0.05" />

                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes pulseStar {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        50% { opacity: 0.2; transform: scale(0.5); }
    }
    .animate-pulse-star {
        animation: pulseStar 1s linear infinite;
    }
</style>
